40 young people took part in the 2017 Leading like Mandela inaugural dialogue and training session

The Mandela Leadership Development Framework with eight components:


A.	Leading Like Mandela;
B.	Mandela Talks;
C.	Research Think Tank;
D.	Conferences, Events, Retreats;
E.	Leaving a Legacy;
F.	Leadership Network;
G.	Leadership Training;
H.	Dialogue Sessions.
